content.rendered:
Directed by Shofela Coker. Raymond Malinga. Ahmed Teilab.

Written by Shofela Coker. Tafadzwa Hove. Raymond Malinga. Terrence Maluleke. Spoek Mathambo. Tshepo Moche. Isaac Mogajane. Ng’endo Mukii. Terence Neale. Pious Nyenyewa. Simangaliso ‘Panda’ Sibaya. Ahmed Teilab. Lesego Vorster. Malcolm Wope.

Cast Florence Kasumba. Hakeem Kae-Kazim. Pearl Thusi. Kehinde Bankole. Lillian Dube. Nasty C.. Tumi Morake. Sheila Munyiva. Clementine Mosimane. Stycie Waweru. Mandisa Nduna. Gigi Lamayne. Tyson Ngubeni . Sne Dladla. Candice Modiselle

Language English.

Producers Matthew Brown. Kaya Kuhn. Vanessa Ann Sinden. Yamen Zakaria. Tendayi Nyeke. Peter Ramsey. Anthony Silverston.

Production Disney Television Animation. Disney+. Splashteam.

No. of Seasons 1

No. of Episodes 10

Status OnGoing (2023–)
